33:41.680 --> 33:44.050
Saya nak cari jurulatih di mana?

33:44.080 --> 33:45.080
Bersemangatlah.

33:50.360 --> 33:51.360
Bersemangatlah.

33:56.070 --> 33:56.830
Penyelia Qian,

33:56.830 --> 33:57.830
