33:57.830 --> 33:58.590
- Baiklah.
- Baik.

33:58.590 --> 33:59.510
Jumpa lagi.

34:01.830 --> 34:03.090
Jumpa lagi, Cikgu Lin.

34:08.929 --> 34:10.820
