36:41.260 --> 36:42.490
- Betul.
- Betul.

36:42.980 --> 36:43.900
Betul.

36:46.280 --> 36:47.230
Baiklah,

36:47.280 --> 36:48.470
saya akan cuba.

37:18.740 --> 37:19.670
